            <title><![CDATA[周一周一，疲惫感+1[困] 搬砖人必备的肩颈操，3个动作拯救肩膀酸痛、脖子僵硬：①回头望月；②旋颈望踵；③雏鸟起飞👇🏻在工位偷偷摸鱼练起来[doge] #小卫唠...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[周一周一，疲惫感+1<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 搬砖人必备的肩颈操，3个动作拯救肩膀酸痛、脖子僵硬：①回头望月；②旋颈望踵；③雏鸟起飞👇🏻在工位偷偷摸鱼练起来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4989852916318373" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hlsdta1odtj20zk0k075k.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/TzNV5LfBlx08bIw5a8JO01041200fz4W0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705396618&amp;ssig=vJ6Q7mu5J2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kPi9qxgRlx08bIw3LFwk010412007u870E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705396618&amp;ssig=90faBtepPD&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5QmSyvjhlx08bIw3uvAY010412004LKQ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705396618&amp;ssig=fWfI%2B82icc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4989852916318373" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
